“扎”，创新 100 余种针法，重建璞真染坊</p>\",\"level\":\"1\",\"name\":\"\\t段银开\",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"0\"} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 13:26:22',31),(221,'非遗展品',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageItemController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/heritage_manage','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":12,\"coverImage\":\"/profile/upload/2025/12/27/R-C_20251227232239A003.jpg\",\"craft\":\"<p><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">核心工艺流程为：</span></p><ol><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">制胎塑形</strong><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">：以纯银熔铸、捶打为薄胎杯身，通过模具或手工调整器型；</span></li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">鎏金装饰</strong><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">：将金汞合金均匀涂抹于杯身纹样区域，经高温烘烤使汞蒸发，金层附着于银胎表面；</span></li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">錾刻纹样</strong><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">：用錾子在杯身、杯沿雕刻白族特色的 “山茶花、洱海波纹” 等图案，部分会辅以镂空工艺增加层次；</span></li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">抛光打磨</strong><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">：用玛瑙刀等工具抛光表面，使银胎与鎏金部分光泽协调，提升质感。</span></li></ol><p><br></p>\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-27 23:25:49\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"description\":\"这是白族传统金属工艺制品，以银为胎、鎏金饰纹，杯身常刻有白族特色的花鸟、几何纹样，兼具实用功能与民族艺术美感，是白族待客礼仪与工艺技艺结合的代表器物。\",\"favoriteCount\":1,\"history\":\"<p><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);\\\">白族金属制器技艺可追溯至南诏时期，当时已出现银器锻造工艺；明清时期，随着白族与中原、东南亚的贸易往来，鎏金技法传入并与本土银器工艺融合，银胎鎏金茶具开始成为贵族与商绅的待客用具；近现代以来，这种茶具既保留了传统纹样的文化符号，也在器型上融入了更贴合日常使用的设计，是白族金属工艺传承与演变的实物体现。</span></p>\",\"isCollected\":true,\"isLiked\":true,\"itemId\":10,\"itemName\":\"白族银胎鎏金茶具\",\"likeCount\":1,\"modelFile\":\"/profile/upload/2025/12/27/teacup_20251227232545A004.glb\",\"params\":{},\"sortOrde','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 13:40:40',15),(222,'非遗展品',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageItemController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/heritage_manage','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":11,\"coverImage\":\"/profile/upload/2025/12/26/木雕02_20251226171042A009.jpg\",\"craft\":\"<p>木雕</p>\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 17:10:57\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"description\":\"木雕\",\"favoriteCount\":1,\"history\":\"<p>木雕</p>\",\"isCollected\":true,\"isLiked\":true,\"itemId\":8,\"itemName\":\"木雕\",\"likeCount\":1,\"params\":{},\"sortOrder\":1,\"status\":0,\"updateBy\":\"\",\"updateTime\":\"2026-01-03 13:40:55\",\"viewCount\":21} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 13:40:55',15),(223,'非遗分类',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageCategoryController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/category','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryCode\":\"CRAFT_ZC\",\"categoryId\":15,\"categoryName\":\"白族三道茶\",\"children\":[],\"createBy\":\"\",\"createTime\":\"2026-01-02 23:36:47\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"params\":{},\"parentId\":1,\"sortOrder\":6,\"status\":0,\"updateBy\":\"\",\"updateTime\":\"2026-01-03 13:42:26\"} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 13:42:26',21),(224,'非遗分类',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageCategoryController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/category','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryCode\":\"FOLK_SDC\",\"categoryId\":15,\"categoryName\":\"白族三道茶\",\"children\":[],\"createBy\":\"\",\"createTime\":\"2026-01-02 23:36:47\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"params\":{},\"parentId\":4,\"sortOrder\":6,\"status\":0,\"updateBy\":\"\",\"updateTime\":\"2026-01-03 13:48:03\"} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 13:48:03',11),(225,'非遗传承人',1,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageInheritorController.add()','POST',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/inheritor','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":10,\"inheritorId\":2,\"introduction\":\"<div class=\\\"ql-code-block-container\\\" spellcheck=\\\"false\\\"><div class=\\\"ql-code-block\\\" data-language=\\\"plain\\\">专注 “染”，开发天然染料，拓展扎染色彩</div></div><p><br></p>\",\"level\":\"2\",\"name\":\"段树坤\",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"0\"} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 14:25:24',36),(226,'非遗传承人',1,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageInheritorController.add()','POST',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/inheritor','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":10,\"inheritorId\":3,\"introduction\":\"<div class=\\\"ql-code-block-container\\\" spellcheck=\\\"false\\\"><div class=\\\"ql-code-block\\\" data-language=\\\"plain\\\">蓝续创始人，打造沉浸式扎染体验 </div></div><p><br></p>\",\"level\":\"3\",\"name\":\"张翰敏\",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"0\"} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 14:26:27',18),(227,'非遗传承人',1,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageInheritorController.add()','POST',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/inheritor','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":40,\"inheritorId\":4,\"introduction\":\"<div class=\\\"ql-code-block-container\\\" spellcheck=\\\"false\\\"><div class=\\\"ql-code-block\\\" data-language=\\\"plain\\\">大理市白族，传承大本曲说唱艺术</div></div><p><br></p>\",\"level\":\"1\",\"name\":\"张亚辉\",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"0\"} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 14:27:09',15),(228,'非遗展品',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageItemController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/heritage_manage','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":15,\"coverImage\":\"/profile/upload/2025/12/26/三道茶_20251226170846A007.jpg\",\"craft\":\"<p>三道茶</p>\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 17:09:15\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"description\":\"三道茶\",\"favoriteCount\":0,\"history\":\"<p>三道茶</p>\",\"isCollected\":false,\"isLiked\":true,\"itemId\":6,\"itemName\":\"三道茶\",\"likeCount\":1,\"params\":{},\"sortOrder\":1,\"status\":0,\"updateBy\":\"\",\"updateTime\":\"2026-01-03 14:30:15\",\"viewCount\":17} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 14:30:15',18),(229,'非遗展品',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageItemController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/heritage_manage','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":11,\"coverImage\":\"/profile/upload/2025/12/26/木雕01_20251226163657A004.jpg\",\"craft\":\"<p>🔨 <strong>匠心独运的五大秘法</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>选材观纹</strong> 🌲：</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span>严格选取大理高海拔地区的<strong>古香樟木</strong>。木材需经“三干三湿”的自然老化处理，确保木性稳定，且自带一种能够防虫避邪的淡淡清香。</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>白描定魂</strong> 🖋️：</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span>老艺人不需图纸，直接在木料上进行“胸有成竹”的构图。每一笔都避开木材的结疤，顺应纹理，确定神态。</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>粗坯开山</strong> 🪚：</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span>使用大号凿子进行“减法艺术”。将多余木块切除，确立作品的空间比例，此时已能看出白族服饰飘逸的轮廓感。</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>多层透雕</strong> 🪡：</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>这是最惊艳的一步！</strong> 艺人要在不到 2 厘米的深度内，雕刻出 3 到 5 层重叠的图案。头饰上的每一朵花瓣、衣襟上的每一根丝线，都由细如毫发的雕刀刻划而成。</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>手工推光</strong> 💎：</li><li data-list=\\\"ordered\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span>拒绝化学漆料。完全依靠天然草木灰和多号棉布进行数万次的物理摩擦，使原木产生一种油脂般的莹润光泽，触感如玉，温润入心。</li></ol>\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 16:37:47\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"description\":\"✨ 一木一世界，雕刻白族魂。\\n本展品是“木雕之乡”剑川的代表作。采用顶级香樟木，通过多层透雕技艺刻画了一位温婉的白族少女。作品将传统民族服饰与现代雕塑审美融合，是研究白族民俗与木艺美学的重要数字资产。🪵\",\"favoriteCount\":1,\"history\":\"<p>📜 <strong>千年技艺的时光沉淀</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>南诏遗风</strong> 🏔️：起源于唐代，作为南诏与大理国时期的宫廷御用技艺，距今已有 1000 多年历史。</li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong>文化交融</strong> 🤝：它不仅保留了白族原始的图腾崇拜，还深度融合了中原汉族的建筑木作工艺','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 14:30:35',22),(230,'非遗分类',1,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageCategoryController.add()','POST',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/category','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryCode\":\"FOLK_DBQ\",\"categoryId\":44,\"categoryName\":\"大本曲\",\"children\":[],\"createTime\":\"2026-01-03 14:32:57\",\"params\":{},\"parentId\":4,\"sortOrder\":4,\"status\":0} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 14:32:57',18),(231,'非遗分类',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageCategoryController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/category','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryCode\":\"FOLK_DBQ\",\"categoryId\":44,\"categoryName\":\"白族大本曲\",\"children\":[],\"createBy\":\"\",\"createTime\":\"2026-01-03 14:32:57\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"params\":{},\"parentId\":4,\"sortOrder\":4,\"status\":0,\"updateBy\":\"\",\"updateTime\":\"2026-01-03 14:34:39\"} ','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-03 14:34:39',16),(232,'非遗传承人',2,'com.ruoyi.heritage.controller.HeritageInheritorController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','研发部门','/heritage/inheritor','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"categoryId\":44,\"createBy\":\"\",\"createTime\":\"2026-01-03 14:27:09\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"inheritorId\":4,\"introduction\":\"<div class=\\\"ql-code-bl